embeds.title: Elaine (Fiche)
embeds.description:
Résumé : Elaine
A strong support/utility character rated S or high-A tier by the community. Wand is a Wind-element DPS with escalating Crit Damage; Staff is a Burst acceleration support that restores magic and protects allies; Book brings Earth Petrify crowd control with team double-damage on Petrified enemies.
